  (text "POWER DELIVERY NETWORK (PDN)\n\nInput Stage:\n• PCIe Slot: 12V @ 12.5A (75W max)\n• 8-pin PEX: 12V @ 40A (225W max)\n• Total Budget: 225W typical, 275W peak\n\nPower Distribution:\n• VCore (0.9V): 12-phase parallel, 210A total\n  - MP5949 PWM Controller\n  - 24x CSD95481RWJ MOSFETs (12 high, 12 low)\n  - 12x 0.47µH Phase Inductors\n  - ~600x MLCCs for decoupling\n\n• VMemory (1.2V): Single phase, 75A\n  - Dedicated buck converter\n  - ~150x MLCCs for HBM3 proximity\n\n• V5 (5.0V): Auxiliary LDO\n  - PTC Fuse 15A\n  - Fan/Sensor supply\n\n• V3.3 & V1.8: Secondary LDOs\n  - I/O and Digital Logic supplies\n\nFault Protection:\n• Soft-start: 100Ω resistor, 500ms ramp\n• OCP: >220A peak threshold\n• OVP: >1.0V Vcore shutdown\n• UVLO: <0.8V emergency shutdown\n• Hold-up Capacitors: 1000µF on 12V rail"
    (at 30.48 50.8) (effects (font (size 2.54 2.54) (thickness 0.254)) (justify left)) (uuid "text_pdn"))

